{"tid":871431,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"間歇性斷食 vs 早餐","createTime":"2018-10-22T02:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T20:39:40.000Z","uid":190141,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b478a39ae6ec35ddaa14afcd4bc9e3c4571dcf06","tid":871431,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n前幾日開始試用16:8間歇性斷食去減肥 發現效果好似幾好<br />\n<br />\n所以想keep住用<br />\n<br />\n但我有個疑問係<br />\n<br />\n我每日大約730-830呢段時間食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n平日返工每日都要早起 放假就話訓到12點 基本上早餐就已經係午餐 所以都隔夠16個鐘<br />\n<br />\n但平日返工7點幾就要醒，如果要keep住16:8既就要skip早餐<br />\n<br />\n咁既情況下，我應該keep番正常三餐去維持代謝，定係照skip早餐keep住16:8既模式會減得好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3286e00dc78e558a029b69fd394796dd1429f0f7","tid":871431,"uid":145221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"skip早餐 <br />\n慢慢身體就會習慣"},{"pid":"a8781f796dc574efeff46d464d12401df2fcaaeb","tid":871431,"uid":103248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"有做運動既話食足3餐有乜所謂<br />\n有食早餐人都精神d啦<br />\n食得健康就減到"},{"pid":"72633498da8eebe9ee97ef8ddee8ec0a3f4966cd","tid":871431,"uid":129961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"be37022020f51e2a857c95f31aa23a0bf7444bfa","tid":871431,"uid":190141,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8781f796dc574efeff46d464d12401df2fcaaeb","tid":871431,"uid":103248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"有做運動既話食足3餐有乜所謂<br />\n有食早餐人都精神d啦<br />\n食得健康就減到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"因為search完見好多研究同實驗證明用間歇性斷食會有效好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時又唔會減、甚至係增加肌肉量"},{"pid":"bc274b29195e2380b789a572722d3f6628adcf06","tid":871431,"uid":190141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3286e0